snippet.title: Puppet Master The Game + Horror Legends Guest Character!
snippet.description:
#PUPPETMASTER #VIDEOGAMES #ASYMMETRICAL

October Games and Full Moon Features join forces to bring some of their most iconic characters into the world of video games! 

Starting NOW you can play RADU from the hit video series SUBSPECIES as a guest character in October Games asymmetrical horror video game HORROR LEGENDS!

Then in late 2022 you'll be able to pull the strings of some of the most deadly Tiny Terrors to ever grace the aisles of your local video store. In Full Moon Feature's and October Games' PUPPET MASTER: THE GAME!!

Play Radu today, and stay tuned for more Puppet Master!
